snippet.title: Verne: the shape of fantasy. Gameplay teaser
snippet.description:
Enjoy our first gameplay teaser from chapter 4! A pixel art narrative game to UNFOLD the boundaries of imagination, based on Jules Verne's world.

Coming 2021 to PC/MAC. 👉 http://www.julesvernegame.com
